                        <li>Price: ₹13–14 lakh</li>
                        <li>Offers smooth drive quality</li>
                        <li>Loaded with smart and connected features</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="subheading">Maruti Swift AMT/CVT</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mileage: ~23–24 km/l</li>
