                        <li>Spacious and easy to maneuver</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="subheading">Dzire AMT</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Price: ~₹8 lakh</li>
                        <li>Offers sedan-like space and comfort</li>
                        <li>Smooth and refined driving experience</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="subheading">Nissan Magnite CVT</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Price: ~₹10 lakh</li>
