                    <ul>
                        <li>Price: ~₹14 lakh</li>
                        <li>Punchy turbo performance</li>
                        <li>Comes with premium features and tech</li>
                    </ul>
         

                <div class="div-line"></div>

                <h3 class="subheading">7. Buyer Trends in 2025</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Urban Shift</span>: Over 60% city buyers now prefer automatics.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Rural Holdout</span>: Manuals still dominate in smaller towns.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">First-Time Buyers</span>: Opting AMTs for ease of driving.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Resale</span>: Automatics now edge ahead in metro markets.</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="div-line"></div>

                <h3 class="subheading">8. Common Questions — Answered!</h3>

                <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq1">
                                Are automatics reliable on Indian roads?
                            </button>
